# Vercel uploads the working directory, and it does NOT read .git/info/exclude —
# so the local-only files kept out of git that way (.claude/CLAUDE.md, the agent
# definitions) were being deployed and served: /.claude/CLAUDE.md returned 200 in
# production. Keep the whole folder off the CDN.
.claude

# Editor/OS noise that has no business on the CDN either.
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
